WEBVTT

00:00:29.908 --> 00:00:33.647
It turns out that tears 
just aren't much help

00:00:33.647 --> 00:00:37.176
when you're trying 
to investigate a genocide.

00:00:37.176 --> 00:00:42.037
The things I had to see, 
and feel and touch

00:00:42.037 --> 00:00:44.864
were pretty unspeakable.

00:00:45.534 --> 00:00:48.891
What I can tell you is this:

00:00:48.891 --> 00:00:50.988
that the Rwandan genocide

00:00:50.988 --> 00:00:56.661
was one of the world's
greatest failures of simple compassion.

